WELCOME TO MY WEBSITE!

https://youtu.be/pM1X1GJ49ek

That is the video link to show full functionality of the website!

TO BEGIN!:

1. download the zip file of this repo to your system

2. Download MAMP and open  http://localhost/phpMyAdmin/

3. Create a new database called learninglist

4. Import learninglist-3-40178155.sql from the zip into the database

5. Install nodeJS into your system https://nodejs.org/en/learn/getting-started/how-to-install-nodejs

6. This is what your.env should look like:

      DB_HOST=<check under MySQL tab when MAMP loads for this info>
      DB_USER=<check under MySQL tab when MAMP loads for this info>
      DB_PASSWORD=<check under MySQL tab when MAMP loads for this info>
      DB_NAME=learninglist
      DB_PORT=<check under MySQL tab when MAMP loads for this info>
      API_PORT=4000
      APP_PORT=3000
      SESSION_SECRET=<see below>

// For added secuirty the website will need a "secret" to run! 

// In terminal do the following: 

// const crypto = require('crypto');
// const secret = crypto.randomBytes(64).toString('hex');
// console.log(secret);

7. Open two terminals 

8. In the first terminal it will run your API so change directory to learninglist/api
    run the command 'npm install'(this will install needed dependecies)
    run command node api.js

9. In the second terminal it will run your APP so change directory to learninglist/app
    run the command 'npm install'(this will install needed dependecies)
    run command node api.js

10. ENJOY THE WEBSITE!


